## Key Concepts
- Event deduplication using tenantId and eventId
- Exactly-once processing via Durable Functions and durable state
- Tenant-scoped Cosmos partitions and region-bound accounts for residency
- Tamper-evident logging and versioned rollback strategy

## Code Example
